quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  47,1,"∆Āeen yeddu…ďe …ďe falii laawol Allah ngol, O bonnii golle ma…ď…ďe …óeen."
  47,2,"GooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen …ďe ngolli golle mo∆ī∆īe, …ďe ngooŇč…óini ko jippinaa kon e Muhammad - on goonga immor…óo e Joomi ma…ď…ďe - O yawtanii …ďe bon…ói ma…ď…ďe …óin, O mo∆ī∆īinii fiyaaku ma…ď…ďe oon."
  47,3,"Ko wa…ói …óuum, ko tawde yeddu…ďe …ďen njokkii mehre nden, gooŇč…óiin…ďe …ďen kan njokki goonga kan immorde e Joomi ma…ď…ďe on. Ko wano nii Allah fiyiranta yim…ďe …ďen yeru ma…ď…ďe …óen."
  47,4,"Si on kawri e yeddu…ďe …ďeen (ka hare), ko soppugol daa…óe …óeen. Haa si on …óu…ó…óinii bargol …ďe, ka…ď…ďon koy…óe …óen. Ko si on mo∆ī∆īora e ma…ď…ďe ngaccitugol …ďe …ďaawo …óuum, maa si ko soktiigu, haa hare ndeen wallina jogaaji mayre. Ko non √Īaawiraa, si Allah no muuyunoo, O wallitotono on e ma…ď…ďe, ko woni tan, ko no O jarribora yoga mon e dow yoga. Waraa…ďe fii Allah …ďeen, pellet, O yeebataa golle ma…ď…ďe …óeen."
  47,5,"Arma O feewna …ďe, O mo∆ī∆īina fiyaaku ma…ď…ďe,"
  47,6,"O naatnya …ďe Aljanna, mo O anndini …ďe fii mum."
  47,7,"Eey mon yo gooŇč…óiin…ďe, si on ngonii walloo…ďe fii Allah, O wallat on, O tabintina teppe mon …óen."
  47,8,"Yeddu…ďe …ďee kan, halkaare woodanii …ďe, O majjinii kadi golle ma…ď…ďe …óeen."
  47,9,"∆äuum le ko tawde …ďe a√Īii ko Allah jippini kon, O bonni golle ma…ď…ďe …óeen."
  47,10,"E …ďee njiilaaki e leydi ndin, …ďe teskoo ko honno battane adinoo…ďe …ďeen wa'unoo? Allah halkuno fii ma…ď…ďe. sugu mum kadi hino woodani yeddu…ďe …ďeen."
  47,11,"Ko wa…ói …óum, ko tawde ko Allah woni gi…óo gooŇč…óiin…ďe …ďeen; hara non yeddu…ďe …ďen, gi…óo (woo) alanaa …ďe."